title: Excitement, boycotts and rainbow protest: Qatar’s World Cup kicks off
description: The 2022 tournament is finally here. But for more than a decade, disquiet over the Gulf state hosting football’s biggest event has been growing. Four people – with very different perspectives – explain their views. Help support our independent journalism at theguardian.com/infocus
